        "TextSection": {
            "TextSectionType": "Definition",
            "Contents": "Infantile cerebral and cerebellar atrophy with postnatal progressive microcephaly is a rare central nervous system malformation syndrome characterized by progressive microcephaly with profound motor delay and intellectual disability associated with hypertonia spasticity clonus and seizures with brain imaging revealing severe cerebral and cerebellar atrophy and poor myelination."
